Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到  會以這種形式相見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都是豚鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市就是實驗動物的飼養場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些小鬼都是家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是眼下  掌握著拯救菲布莉的關鍵的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵  好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗動物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是泰瑞絲緹娜·木原·萊夫雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦野也下来游嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是面子問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被別人利用了還忍氣吞聲的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這個圈子  被小瞧了就沒有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.88,small,NTP,0,0,0,,你不游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.84,small,NTP,0,0,0,,我樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被假消息牽著鼻子走  還不都是你的責任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑什麼要我們來給你擦屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是不給報酬  就不要發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不也說過被弄得團團轉還一肚子火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞一場大龍鳳也沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦  麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧…雖然沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去活動活動筋骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這副嘴臉變得不錯了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒少經歷這座城市的黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對深深的黑暗感到絕望和膽怯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後呢  有否因此而詛咒這座學院都市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後發現我所說的話是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園都市是實驗場地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生全都是豚鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  想問我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是想讓我摸摸頭給予你安慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救我一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她名字叫菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個人造的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都不做的話她只剩下72小時的命了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道菲布莉是暗部的人製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你應該知道點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多克隆體被殺害還真有臉說出這種天真的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的那個什麼小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在這座城市的黑暗中誕生的一隻豚鼠罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼被黑暗吞噬成為家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼將黑暗打破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外沒有任何辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實窺探過你所說的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受到了相當的震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也自暴自棄過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我從裡面救出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是在這座城市裡邂逅的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有許多對我十分重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這座城市的話  我是不會遇到他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也有不少讓人生氣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要討厭這座學院城市我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰製造了菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的目的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是騙你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼要告訴你真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的話  你又能相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我決定相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒放哦  巧克力糖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是相信我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了相信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我關於菲布莉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有什麼要告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你告訴我  否則我就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吵  快給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  告訴我關於菲布莉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱米卡萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人應該這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱米卡萊特  指的是菲布莉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時應該只有理論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說那幾個小少年成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人就是製造了菲布莉的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要突顯一下自己的存在感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突顯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個活動快要開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學究會?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂突顯存在感指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了那麼一點事讓菲布莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.96,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(565,646)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被選中的超能力者大人才能說出的大話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  你給我好好記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座學園都市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.97,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(563,645)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要將超能力者這個名片發出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算像你這樣的實驗動物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會有許多好朋友向你靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連實驗動物都當不了的那些人的黑暗是有多深不可測
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要嚇得尿褲子哦  臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  你去找那位泰瑞絲緹娜小姐了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事出突然  因此沒和大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個凱米卡萊特就是菲布莉的正式稱呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群人想要在學究會搞什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方並沒有說得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要是婚后她們看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個談到菲布莉的人也去了學究會會場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上最近將會舉辦的活動  我猜應該就那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是醫院的那位醫生介紹你去見泰瑞絲緹娜小姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子長得像一個可愛的吉祥物  到底是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位醫生還說過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說現有的糖能支撐菲布莉生命的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約72小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,72小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我篩選一下學究會的參加者試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉辦方以及參加的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  醒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  午安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天帶了一些好東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道發現什麼線索了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸…不是…關於那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們幾乎一直都在找那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是還沒有任何發現…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不過  我們一定能找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們今天來是有關別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想給菲布莉妹妹一份禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我們看到了一件挺可愛的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該會很襯菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們說這是送給菲布莉的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那打開看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給菲布莉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子  湾内  泡浮謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必言謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是見證友誼的小禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臉好紅  難道是發燒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋暈暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃糖吧  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻不容緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在學究會會場看到的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  湾内  泡浮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這照片是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去年學究會的參加者名單裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有富春樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在前年的學究會獲得了最優秀獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且幾乎每年都是名列前茅的獲獎者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長年在學究會名列前茅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在學園都市也是屈指可數的才子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他啊  完全不認識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  果然和高等級能力者相比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才子就顯得毫不起眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連實驗動物都當不了的傢伙們的黑暗是有多深不可測
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這個人今年好像沒參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄泉川老師也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「往年的獲獎參加者今年都沒怎麼來」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯獨今年  有好多人都沒參加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  這當中可能有他的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有相關數據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只剩下第一實驗室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  看不見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  不熱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食慾也恢復了  姑且可以鬆口氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春  你一直在調查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得閒不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫有富的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前好像自主退學了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧  他都聰明到能拿獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這麼有才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是用在正道上該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會想要擄走菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會又是什麼黑暗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然還是頭一次知道學究會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過一想到有人就算沒有能力也在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中還是略感欣慰的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  黄泉川老師  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來目前的情況還是因為證據不足而無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這也是意料之中的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然遭到了施壓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.99,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(563,645)}<Antiskill>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就明白警備員是無法依靠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人?  你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在想泰瑞絲緹娜說的那番話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.00,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(747.2,641.6)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一說常盤台的超電磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的人應該不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不少人是因此而認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.39,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(694.4,643.2)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不是超能力者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許就無法和黒子以及大家成為好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.99,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(787,639)}<LEVEL 5>                               <Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黒子仰慕的並不是超能力者——常盤台的超電磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是有些小魯莽而且興趣低齡向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為學妹著想待人溫柔的御坂美琴姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黒子  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別趁機來熊抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  別說我的興趣低齡向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…在施以懲戒時毫不留情的這一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是黒子最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Study Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  這家公司的董事當中有一個叫有富春樹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家公司是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.74,small,NTP,0,0,0,,來  菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.70,small,NTP,0,0,0,,呱太在哪隻手裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.45,small,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.99,small,NTP,0,0,0,,猜對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製藥以及各種廣域科研
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那所謂的可疑設施是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Study Corporation在第十七學區擁有的工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人在意的是  雖然是不起眼的舊工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻以高價將其買下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工廠的話…是不是製造菲布莉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定那個糖也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.81,small,NTP,0,0,0,,哪隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.56,small,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要是能知道成份的數據的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來直接潛入調查是最簡單快捷的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說時間也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓緊考慮如何改善菲布莉的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是需要那個糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要獲得配方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不容有失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這關乎到菲布莉的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那座橋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的夢想是不會失去任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都笑著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…為了讓其實現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細一想  那番話還真是隨意得牽強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒想過萬一沒實現又該怎麼辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有堅信會實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一實驗室出現入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵者  是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦系統已經由SHIFT-A進入了警戒模式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為第一實驗室并沒有好好設置情報防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所謂的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有人查上門來也沒什麼大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當下就算查到了第一實驗室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會對我們的計劃造成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼見不得光的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮的數據全都已經轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的也只有那個中和劑的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去第一實驗室?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會和入侵者一起被驅除的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒打算以身犯險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今計劃近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了確保不出萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去確認下安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一個人都沒有  靠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超像是假情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去後真的能得到報酬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼她們會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是知道我會來  特意埋伏在此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子也不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道和菲布莉的製造者是敵對關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗部內部的鬥爭之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.66,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,645)}<AIM  Stalker>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有滝壺的「能力追蹤」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能追蹤曾一度記錄到的能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來  玩偷襲是行不通的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:31.17,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(900.8,643.2)}<Powered Suit>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道有人用念力在操縱無人駕駛的驅動鎧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是附近沒有人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠程操作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可就算是遠程也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.55,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(654.4,644.8)}<Powered Suit>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在駆動鎧裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和構成菲布莉身體物質的成份是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那根頭髮是作為能力的接收器的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  如此龐大數量憑一人操控的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.86,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,648)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那應該是超能力者級別的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  那根頭髮的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像是游泳游太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  氣死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  滝壺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺  還有誰在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  流了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滝壺  你還是別游了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群傢伙還真是暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子  可能什麼都沒留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡面有電源運作的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你稍有動作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和你有關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是他們的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你把我的名字告訴菲布莉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中和劑的數據在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中和劑?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那些糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在應該還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為覺得對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  是我把你的名字告訴菲布莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為想到只有你值得依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我想得過於天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天在這個第一實驗室發生的騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及在這遇見你  實屬幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下菲布莉就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要將她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個配方是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們救不了菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來加個保險是正確的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放走了菲布莉的果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅知道了叛徒是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還遇見了大名人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得沒錯  今天真走運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.48,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,640)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們第一次面對面吧  超電磁砲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你那採集到的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了我們不少忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是有富春樹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意到訪是為了拯救我們的作品——菲布莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作品?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉果然是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好不要使用電擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道想將真的配方也一起毀掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.43,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,641.6)}<Railgun>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個給超電磁砲注射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不讓她動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死不了人的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果你老實聽從命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個給你也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為它對我們已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了救菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.14,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(621,646)}<LEVEL 5>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來連超能力者也無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經遵從你的命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.44,0:23:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  對哈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉只不過是備用品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,備用品?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我們偉大的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍妮的備用品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和你有關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To tell the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來話長了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這真的就太長了
